CERVICAL CANCER CLASSIFICATION USING DEEP LEARNING
This project focuses on detecting and classifying cervical cancer using deep learning techniques.
A trained model (NASNetMobile) is used to predict cancer classes from medical images.

PROJECT STRUCTURE
MPDL03/
│
├── Code/
│   ├── app.py
│   ├── static/
│   ├── templates/
│   ├── test/
│   └── Untitled.ipynb
│
├── Documents/
│   ├── MPDL03.docx
│   └── MPDL03_Final.docx
│
├── NASNetMobile_cancer.h5   # Trained model
├── Enhancing_Cervical_Cancer_Classification.pdf

